## Architecture Overview

```
┌──────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌───────────────┐
│   Network    │────►│  SCM        │────►│  Graph        │
│  Generators  │     │  Builder    │     │  Decomposition│
└──────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └───────┬───────┘
                                                 │
                     ┌───────────────┐           │
                     │  Instruments  │           ▼
                     │  (CDS, IRS…)  │   ┌───────────────┐
                     └───────┬───────┘   │  Causal       │
                             │           │  Polytope LP  │
                             ▼           └───────┬───────┘
                     ┌───────────────┐           │
                     │  Junction-    │           ▼
                     │  Tree Engine  │   ┌───────────────┐
                     └───────┬───────┘   │  Bound        │
                             │           │  Composition  │
                             ▼           └───────┬───────┘
                     ┌───────────────┐           │
                     │  SMT          │           ▼
                     │  Verifier     │   ┌───────────────┐
                     └───────────────┘   │  MCTS         │
                                         │  Adversarial  │
                     ┌───────────────┐   │  Search       │
                     │  Contagion    │   └───────┬───────┘
                     │  Models       │           │
                     └───────────────┘           ▼
                                         ┌───────────────┐
                     ┌───────────────┐   │  Evaluation   │
                     │  Data /       │   │  & Metrics    │
                     │  Serialization│   └───────────────┘
                     └───────────────┘
```

### Module Map

| Module | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| `network` | `causalbound/network/` | Network topology generation, analysis, calibration |
| `scm` | `causalbound/scm/` | Structural Causal Model construction and causal discovery |
| `graph` | `causalbound/graph/` | Tree decomposition and graph partitioning |
| `polytope` | `causalbound/polytope/` | Causal-polytope LP solver with column generation |
| `composition` | `causalbound/composition/` | Bound composition theorem and propagation |
| `junction` | `causalbound/junction/` | Junction-tree exact inference engine |
| `smt` | `causalbound/smt/` | Streaming SMT verification with Z3 |
| `mcts` | `causalbound/mcts/` | MCTS adversarial search with causal UCB |
| `contagion` | `causalbound/contagion/` | Financial contagion models (DebtRank, cascades) |
| `instruments` | `causalbound/instruments/` | Financial instrument models (CDS, IRS, repos) |
| `evaluation` | `causalbound/evaluation/` | Benchmarks, crisis reconstruction, metrics |
| `data` | `causalbound/data/` | Serialization, caching, checkpointing |

